'''Danial Eiri''' ({{langx|fa|دانیال ایری}}; born 26 October 2003) is an Iranian professional footballer who plays as a [[defender (association football)|defender]] for [[Persian Gulf Pro League]] side [[Malavan F.C.|Malavan]], on loan from [[Zob Ahan Esfahan F.C.|Zob Ahan]], and the [[Iran national football team|Iran national team]].

==Club career==
On 19 January 2025, Eiri joined [[Malavan F.C.|Malavan]], on loan from [[Zob Ahan Esfahan F.C.|Zob Ahan]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Danial Eiri at Soccerway |url=https://www.soccerway.com/player/eiri-danial/hxpX9EZf/transfers/ |website=Soccerway |access-date=2 June 2026}}</ref>

==International career==
In 2023, Eiri was part of the [[Iran national under-20 football team|Iran under-20 national team]] squad at the [[2023 AFC U-20 Asian Cup]] in Uzbekistan,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.iribnews.ir/fa/news/3748305/%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%A7%D9%85%DB%8C-%DB%B5%DB%B0-%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B2%DB%8C%DA%A9%D9%86-%D9%86%D9%87%D8%A7%DB%8C%DB%8C-%D8%A8%D8%B1%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D8%AD%D8%B6%D9%88%D8%B1-%D8%AF%D8%B1-%D8%AC%D8%A7%D9%85-%D9%85%D9%84%D8%AA%E2%80%8C%D9%87%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D9%81%D9%88%D8%AA%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%84-%D8%B2%DB%8C%D8%B1-%DB%B2%DB%B0-%D8%B3%D8%A7%D9%84|title=مشخص شدن اسامی 50 بازیکناسامی ۵۰ بازیکن نهایی برای حضور در جام ملت‌های فوتبال زیر ۲۰ سال|trans-title=The names of the final 50 players who participate in the Under-20 Nations Cup|publisher=[[Islamic Republic of Iran Broadcasting|IRIB]]|date=9 February 2023|language=fa}}</ref> and was later selected for the [[Iran national under-23 football team|under-23 national team]]'s squad for the [[2026 AFC U-23 Asian Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web |last= |first= |date=23 December 2025 |title=فهرست ۲۳ نفره تیم ملی امید برای اردوی امارات و جام ملت‌های آسیا |url=https://the-ffiri.com/fa/news/28943/%D9%81%D9%87%D8%B1%D8%B3%D8%AA-%DB%B2%DB%B3-%D9%86%D9%81%D8%B1%D9%87-%D8%AA%DB%8C%D9%85-%D9%85%D9%84%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D9%85%DB%8C%D8%AF-%D8%A8%D8%B1%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%AF%D9%88%DB%8C-%D8%A7%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D9%88-%D8%AC%D8%A7%D9%85-%D9%85%D9%84%D8%AA%E2%80%8C%D9%87%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D8%A2%D8%B3%DB%8C%D8%A7 |access-date= |website=Iranian Football Federation |language=fa}}</ref>

He was first invited to an [[Iran national football team|Iran national team]] training camp in March 2025.<ref>{{cite web |title=دانیال ایری ؛ مدافع آینده‌دار فوتبال ایران به اردوی تیم ملی دعوت شد |url=https://www.danshjoyan-torkman.ir/danial-eyri-team-melli/ |website=اولین پایگاه اطلاع رسانی دانشجویان ترکمن |access-date=2 June 2026 |language=fa-IR |date=15 March 2025}}</ref> In March 2026, he was supposed to travel with Iran for the 2026 [[Jordan International Tournament]], but was unable to join them due to issues relating to his military service, he was replaced in the team by [[Aria Yousefi]].<ref>{{cite web |title=عجیب‌ترین عضو تیم ملی فوتبال ایران! |url=https://www.varzesh3.com/news/2351432/عجیب-ترین-عضو-تیم-ملی-فوتبال-ایران |website=ورزش سه |access-date=2 June 2026 |language=fa |date=30 March 2026 |trans-title=The strangest member of the Iranian national football team!}}</ref> 

On 16 May, Eiri was included in Iran's 30-man preliminary squad for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]],<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.isna.ir/news/1405022615362/%D9%84%DB%8C%D8%B3%D8%AA-%DB%B3%DB%B0-%D9%86%D9%81%D8%B1%D9%87-%D8%AA%DB%8C%D9%85-%D9%85%D9%84%DB%8C-%D8%A8%D8%B1%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D8%AC%D8%A7%D9%85-%D8%AC%D9%87%D8%A7%D9%86%DB%8C-%DB%B2%DB%B0%DB%B2%DB%B6 |title=فهرست ۳۰ نفره تیم ملی برای جام جهانی ۲۰۲۶ اعلام شد |trans-title=Iran's 30-man squad for the 2026 World Cup announced |work=[[Iranian Students' News Agency]] |date=May 16, 2026 |access-date=June 1, 2026 |language=fa}}</ref> before being officially selected for the final squad on 1 June.<ref>{{cite web |title=Iran drop Azmoun as Taremi leads 26-man World Cup squad in US |url=https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/iran-drop-azmoun-taremi-leads-26-man-world-cup-squad-us-2026-06-01/ |website=[[Reuters]] |access-date=1 June 2026 |date=1 June 2026}}</ref>

